3.
Description 
                  ​3.1.​         ​Please give a brief description of your study, including some 
background, the purpose of the of the study, or broad research questions. 
                  ​3.2.​         ​Example​: Though there is strong evidence to suggest that sugar 
affects taste preferences, the effect has never been demonstrated in brownies. 
Therefore, we will measure taste preference for four different levels of sugar 
concentration in a standard brownie recipe to determine if the effect exists in this 
