               ​16.2.​         ​Example:​ We manipulated the percentage of sugar by mass added 
to brownies. The four levels of this categorical variable are: 15%, 20%, 25%, or 
40% cane sugar by mass. 
               ​16.3.​         ​More information​: For any experimental manipulation, you should 
give a precise definition of each manipulated variable. This must include a 
