STATISTICAL MODELS: 
  
  
We will run a 2 (level: category (no brand) vs. brand; between-subject factor) × 2 (product type: 
utilitarian vs. symbolic; within-subject factor) mixed ANOVA on the difference scores (averaged 
for each subject and each product type). 
